{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_04_01",
  "title": "fran 1話 そうなんですか？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "海……綺麗だなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ocean… it's so beautiful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3766.6666667,
          "startTime": 4.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 4.4977098862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、何ぼーっとしてるんですか\nきびきび動かないと飢え死にしますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san‚ what are you daydreaming about?\nIf you don't move quickly‚ you'll starve to death‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですよね。そうなんですよね、はは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… you're right. That's true‚ haha…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.1627209584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 19.6653278906
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（franさんの言葉は、冗談じゃなくて事実だ）\n（なんで、こんなことになったんだろう……？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（fran-san's words aren't a joke‚ they're a fact.）\n（How did it come to this…?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.6333323161,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――生放送特番の収録後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――After the live special broadcast",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.6287969191,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 29.1621299982
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "franさん。番組宣伝用の撮影、お疲れ様でした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san. Thank you for the work on the promotional shoot for the program.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.1287966649,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 34.2941480398
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "昨日はスカッとしましたから、撮影もうまくいきました\nは～、とってもいい気分！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I felt great yesterday‚ so the shoot went well too.\nAh‚ it feels so good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 42.0460750978
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "（嫌がらせをしてきたアイドルをものの見事に）\n（叩きのめしたからな……三人とも明らかに上機嫌だ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They thoroughly beat the idol who was bullying them…）\n（All three of them are clearly in a good mood.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6342157524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 49.6274355014
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "レギュラーになれましたし\n番宣も任せてもらえて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We became regulars‚\ngot to do the promo too‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.5666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "それに、この無人島は雰囲気がいいから\n撮影も楽しかったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and this deserted island has such a great atmosphere.\nThe shoot was really fun.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.4333315532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "潮が引いている時は徒歩で渡れる、っていうのが\nまた趣がありますよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's quaint how you can walk over\nwhen the tide is low‚ isn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.0666648865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 65.4116251705
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "それじゃあ、そろそろホテルに戻って\nスタッフのみなさんと打ち上げをしましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's head back to the hotel\nand have a wrap party with the staff.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6999928791,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……せっかく来たんですし\nもうちょっと見て回って来てもいいですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… since we're here‚\ncan I walk around a bit more?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 76.9520727553
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "私、打ち上げもパーティーも苦手ですから\nあんまり出たくないんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm not good with parties or celebrations.\nI don't feel like to attend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1666539509,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、そういえば前に聞いたような……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ now that you mention it‚ I think I've heard that before…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5325725314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 87.1808899003
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ファッション関係の集まりなら\n人脈作りをするために行かざるを得ないんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If it's a fashion gathering‚\nI have to go for networking purposes‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.5666503906,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "こういう番組の打ち上げなら\nmihoとkanaがいるじゃないですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For a show's wrap party‚\nwe have miho and kana.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.9666514079,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 98.423498384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "あの二人なら面倒な人付き合いもそつなくこなしますし\n任せてしまって問題ないと思います",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Those two can handle the socializing well.\nI think it's fine to leave it to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.7666570028,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6133.333841999999,
          "startTime": 108.8999908448
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（普段はあんなに仲が悪いのに、仕事に関しては）\n（信頼し合ってるっていうのも不思議だよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It's strange how they usually don't get along‚）\n（but they trust each other when it comes to work）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.9999852498,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 112.627649919
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "今の時刻は……うん、あんまり株価も動かないだろうし\nちょっとくらいぶらついても大丈夫かな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right now… yeah‚ the stock market isn't moving much.\nIt should be fine to wander around for a bit.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6666590374,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 121.4628426311
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。それなら俺が付き添います\nmihoさんとkanaさんにも伝えておきますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. In that case‚ I'll accompany you.\nI'll let miho-san and kana-san know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.6666534424,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "別に私一人でもいいんですけど……ま、いいか\nそれじゃあ先にスタッフさんに挨拶だけしておきますか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even though I can manage alone… well‚ alright.\nShall we greet the staff first?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.1666468303,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5278.411872999982,
          "startTime": 139.4450587033
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 139.2117248613
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "本当に海が綺麗ね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The sea is really beautiful…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3450642982,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "普段、節約のために旅行を控えてるから\nこういう時じゃないとのびのび出来ないんですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I usually avoid traveling to save money‚\nso I can only relax on occasions like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.0666468303,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "beach",
      "startTime": 150.6425563334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_04_01-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "あ、見て下さいよ、あの植物\n都内じゃ絶対見かけないですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ look at that plant.\nYou’d never see that in the city.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.4999893189,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
